{
  "video_id": "NL0uxDscjdo",
  "title": "How cults rewire the brain | Diane Benscoter",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 18330.0,
      "end_time": 22330.0,
      "text": "My journey to coming here today"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 22330.0,
      "end_time": 24330.0,
      "text": "started in 1974."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 24330.0,
      "end_time": 27330.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s me with the funny gloves."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 27330.0,
      "end_time": 30330.0,
      "text": "I was 17 and going on a peace walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30330.0,
      "end_time": 33330.0,
      "text": "What I didn&#39;t know though, was most of those people, standing there"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33330.0,
      "end_time": 35330.0,
      "text": "with me, were Moonies."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35330.0,
      "end_time": 39330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39330.0,
      "end_time": 41330.0,
      "text": "And within a week"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41330.0,
      "end_time": 43330.0,
      "text": "I had come to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43330.0,
      "end_time": 46330.0,
      "text": "that the second coming of Christ had occurred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46330.0,
      "end_time": 48330.0,
      "text": "that it was Sun Myung Moon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48330.0,
      "end_time": 52330.0,
      "text": "and that I had been specially chosen and prepared by God"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52330.0,
      "end_time": 54330.0,
      "text": "to be his disciple."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54330.0,
      "end_time": 56330.0,
      "text": "Now as cool as that sounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56330.0,
      "end_time": 58330.0,
      "text": "my family was not that thrilled with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58330.0,
      "end_time": 60330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60330.0,
      "end_time": 62330.0,
      "text": "And they tried everything they could to get me out of there."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62330.0,
      "end_time": 64330.0,
      "text": "There was an underground railroad of sorts"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64330.0,
      "end_time": 67330.0,
      "text": "that was going on during those years. Maybe some of you remember it."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67330.0,
      "end_time": 70330.0,
      "text": "They were called deprogrammers."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70330.0,
      "end_time": 76330.0,
      "text": "And after about five long years"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76330.0,
      "end_time": 78330.0,
      "text": "my family had me deprogrammed."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78330.0,
      "end_time": 83330.0,
      "text": "And I then became a deprogrammer."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 83330.0,
      "end_time": 85330.0,
      "text": "I started going out on cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85330.0,
      "end_time": 89330.0,
      "text": "And after about five years of doing this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89330.0,
      "end_time": 93330.0,
      "text": "I was arrested for kidnapping."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93330.0,
      "end_time": 95330.0,
      "text": "Most of the cases I went out on"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95330.0,
      "end_time": 97330.0,
      "text": "were called involuntary."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97330.0,
      "end_time": 99330.0,
      "text": "What happened was that the family"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99330.0,
      "end_time": 102330.0,
      "text": "had to get their loved ones some safe place somehow."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102330.0,
      "end_time": 106330.0,
      "text": "And so they took them to some safe place."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106330.0,
      "end_time": 109330.0,
      "text": "And we would come in and talk to them, usually for about a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109330.0,
      "end_time": 113330.0,
      "text": "And so after this happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113330.0,
      "end_time": 117330.0,
      "text": "I decided it was a good time to turn my back on this work."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117330.0,
      "end_time": 122330.0,
      "text": "And about 20 years went by."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 122330.0,
      "end_time": 125330.0,
      "text": "There was a burning question though that would not leave me."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 125330.0,
      "end_time": 128329.0,
      "text": "And that was, \"How did this happen to me?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128330.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131330.0,
      "text": "And in fact, what did happen to my brain?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131330.0,
      "end_time": 134330.0,
      "text": "Because something did."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134330.0,
      "end_time": 136330.0,
      "text": "And so I decided to write a book, a memoir,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 136330.0,
      "end_time": 139330.0,
      "text": "about this decade of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139330.0,
      "end_time": 141330.0,
      "text": "And toward the end of writing that book"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141330.0,
      "end_time": 143330.0,
      "text": "there was a documentary that came out."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 143330.0,
      "end_time": 145330.0,
      "text": "It was on Jonestown."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 145330.0,
      "end_time": 150330.0,
      "text": "And it had a chilling effect on me."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 150330.0,
      "end_time": 153330.0,
      "text": "These are the dead in Jonestown."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 153330.0,
      "end_time": 155330.0,
      "text": "About 900 people died that day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155330.0,
      "end_time": 158330.0,
      "text": "most of them taking their own lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158330.0,
      "end_time": 162330.0,
      "text": "Women gave poison to their babies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162330.0,
      "end_time": 167330.0,
      "text": "and watched foam come from their mouths as they died."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 167330.0,
      "end_time": 170330.0,
      "text": "The top picture is a group of Moonies"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 170330.0,
      "end_time": 173330.0,
      "text": "that have been blessed by their messiah."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 173330.0,
      "end_time": 176330.0,
      "text": "Their mates were chosen for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176330.0,
      "end_time": 180330.0,
      "text": "The bottom picture is Hitler youth."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180330.0,
      "end_time": 184330.0,
      "text": "This is the leg of a suicide bomber."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 184330.0,
      "end_time": 186330.0,
      "text": "The thing I had to admit to myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 186330.0,
      "end_time": 189330.0,
      "text": "with great repulsion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 189330.0,
      "end_time": 191330.0,
      "text": "was that I get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 191330.0,
      "end_time": 194330.0,
      "text": "I understand how this could happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 194330.0,
      "end_time": 197330.0,
      "text": "I understand how someone&#39;s brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 197330.0,
      "end_time": 200330.0,
      "text": "how someone&#39;s mind can come to the place"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 200330.0,
      "end_time": 202330.0,
      "text": "where it makes sense --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202330.0,
      "end_time": 205330.0,
      "text": "in fact it would be wrong, when your brain is working like that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 205330.0,
      "end_time": 211330.0,
      "text": "not to try to save the world through genocide."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211330.0,
      "end_time": 214330.0,
      "text": "And so what is this? How does this work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 214330.0,
      "end_time": 218330.0,
      "text": "And how I&#39;ve come to view what happened to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 218330.0,
      "end_time": 221330.0,
      "text": "is a viral, memetic infection."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221330.0,
      "end_time": 223330.0,
      "text": "For those of you who aren&#39;t familiar with memetics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223330.0,
      "end_time": 225330.0,
      "text": "a meme has been defined as"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 225330.0,
      "end_time": 227330.0,
      "text": "an idea that replicates in the human brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 227330.0,
      "end_time": 232330.0,
      "text": "and moves from brain to brain like a virus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 232330.0,
      "end_time": 235330.0,
      "text": "much like a virus. The way a virus works is --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 235330.0,
      "end_time": 240330.0,
      "text": "it can infect and do the most damage to someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 240330.0,
      "end_time": 244330.0,
      "text": "who has a compromised immune system."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 244330.0,
      "end_time": 248330.0,
      "text": "In 1974, I was young, I was naive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 248330.0,
      "end_time": 250330.0,
      "text": "and I was pretty lost in my world."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 250330.0,
      "end_time": 253330.0,
      "text": "I was really idealistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 253330.0,
      "end_time": 257330.0,
      "text": "These easy ideas to complex questions are very appealing"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 257329.0,
      "end_time": 260329.0,
      "text": "when you are emotionally vulnerable."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 260329.0,
      "end_time": 263330.0,
      "text": "What happens is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 263330.0,
      "end_time": 265330.0,
      "text": "circular logic takes over."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 265330.0,
      "end_time": 267330.0,
      "text": "\"Moon is one with God."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 267330.0,
      "end_time": 271330.0,
      "text": "God is going to fix all the problems in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 271330.0,
      "end_time": 273330.0,
      "text": "All I have to do is humbly follow."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 273330.0,
      "end_time": 275330.0,
      "text": "Because God is going to stop war and hunger --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 275330.0,
      "end_time": 277330.0,
      "text": "all these things I wanted to do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 277330.0,
      "end_time": 279330.0,
      "text": "all I have to do is humbly follow."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 279330.0,
      "end_time": 282330.0,
      "text": "Because after all, God is [working through] the messiah. He&#39;s going to fix all this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282330.0,
      "end_time": 285330.0,
      "text": "It becomes impenetrable."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 285330.0,
      "end_time": 288330.0,
      "text": "And the most dangerous part of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 288330.0,
      "end_time": 291330.0,
      "text": "is that is creates \"us\" and \"them,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 291330.0,
      "end_time": 293330.0,
      "text": "\"right\" and \"wrong,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 293330.0,
      "end_time": 297330.0,
      "text": "\"good\" and \"evil.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 297330.0,
      "end_time": 301330.0,
      "text": "And it makes anything possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 301330.0,
      "end_time": 308330.0,
      "text": "makes anything rationalizable."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308330.0,
      "end_time": 310330.0,
      "text": "And the thing is, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 310330.0,
      "end_time": 312330.0,
      "text": "if you looked at my brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312330.0,
      "end_time": 314330.0,
      "text": "during those years in the Moonies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 314330.0,
      "end_time": 317330.0,
      "text": "neuroscience is expanding exponentially,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 317330.0,
      "end_time": 319330.0,
      "text": "as Ray Kurzweil said yesterday. Science is expanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 319330.0,
      "end_time": 322330.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re beginning to look inside the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 322330.0,
      "end_time": 324330.0,
      "text": "And so if you looked at my brain, or any brain that&#39;s infected with"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 324330.0,
      "end_time": 327330.0,
      "text": "a viral memetic infection like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 327330.0,
      "end_time": 329330.0,
      "text": "and compared it to anyone in this room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 329330.0,
      "end_time": 331330.0,
      "text": "or anyone who uses critical thinking on a regular basis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 331330.0,
      "end_time": 336330.0,
      "text": "I am convinced it would look very, very different."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 336330.0,
      "end_time": 339330.0,
      "text": "And that, strange as it may sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 339330.0,
      "end_time": 341330.0,
      "text": "gives me hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 341330.0,
      "end_time": 343330.0,
      "text": "And the reason that gives me hope"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 343330.0,
      "end_time": 346330.0,
      "text": "is that the first thing is to admit"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 346330.0,
      "end_time": 349330.0,
      "text": "that we have a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 349330.0,
      "end_time": 352330.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s a human problem. It&#39;s a scientific problem, if you will."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 352330.0,
      "end_time": 356330.0,
      "text": "It happens in the human brain. There is no evil force out there to get us."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 356330.0,
      "end_time": 360330.0,
      "text": "And so this is something that, through research and education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 360330.0,
      "end_time": 363330.0,
      "text": "I believe that we can solve."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 363330.0,
      "end_time": 371330.0,
      "text": "And so the first step is to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 371330.0,
      "end_time": 373330.0,
      "text": "that we can do this together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 373330.0,
      "end_time": 376330.0,
      "text": "and that there is no \"us\" and \"them.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 376330.0,
      "end_time": 378330.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}